T02TD1631E:245a-0: @245a pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha la bstod pa bzhugs /
T02TD1631E:245a-2: # // dpal ldan rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1631E:245a-4: ye shes lnga dang sku gsum nyid //
T02TD1631E:245a-5: 'gro ba skyo ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1631E:245a-6: ji snyed rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1631E:245a-7: kun du rtog pa 'ching gcod cing //
T02TD1631E:245a-9: de snyed rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1631E:245a-10: gnyis med ye shes mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1631E:245a-11: lhan cig skyes pa'i ro snyoms shing //
T02TD1631E:245a-12: bdag med ngo bo phyag rgya che //
T02TD1631E:245a-14: byang chub sems mchog rnam par dag /'gyur ba med pa rdo rje'i dbyings /
T02TD1631E:245a-15: mi bskyod rdo rje ye shes che //
T02TD1631E:245a-17: mchog sbyin ma ni bde ba che //
T02TD1631E:245a-18: mi zad rdo rje nor bu'i dbyings //
T02TD1631E:245a-19: bla na med pa'i dbang bskur ba //
T02TD1631E:245a-21: dri med chos ni rnam par dag / sku gsung thugs ni mtshan ma bral //
T02TD1631E:245a-22: dri med ye shes che bsnyems pa //
T02TD1631E:245a-24: rdo rje las ni thogs pa med //
T02TD1631E:245a-25: rnal 'byor dbang phyugs 'gro ba'i ma mgon //
T02TD1631E:245a-26: nan tan ye shes che ba bsnyems pa //
T02TD1631E:245a-28: dpal ma h'a m'a y'a'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha la bstod pa /
T02TD1631E:245a-29: slob dpon chen po ku ku ri pas zhal gzigs pa'i tshe bstod pa'o//
